title.rendered: 48 rolls x Gentility Premium 2ply 700 sheet Toilet Tissues

content.rendered:
75% more toilet tissue on standard roll size keeps maintenance low
Larger roll still works in standard spindle bathroom fittings

  • Individually wrapped toilet roll
  • 700 sheets per roll
  • 2 ply
  • White virgin pulp
  • 48 rolls/ carton
  • Carton size: 47.5 x 35.5 x 42cm
  • 14.5gsm
